{"tid":661112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Jollibee收購添好運","createTime":"2018-05-11T09:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T13:12:21.000Z","uid":84633,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d700bd50fbbd2897e7debcd4a515260025e40b12","tid":661112,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"近期在香港快速擴張的菲律賓炸雞連鎖店Jollibee（快樂蜂），計劃以3,350萬美元（約2.6億港元）收購迷芝蓮一星、本港著名點心店添好運的亞太區特許經營權。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓上市的Jollibee在當地交易所刊發通告，表示與新加坡私募基金Titan Dining簽署協議，收購後者持有的Tim Ho Wan Pte. Ltd以及附屬公司Dimsum Pte Ltd。<br />\n<br />\n賓賓又贏！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/187371/jollibee收購添好運-香港以外亞太特許經營權\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F187371%2Fjollibee%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E6%B7%BB%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%9E%E5%A4%AA%E7%89%B9%E8%A8%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%87%9F%E6%AC%8A&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e96919b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/187371/jollibee收購添好運-香港以外亞太特許經營權</a>"},{"pid":"1d701897fb1498cb600427170913559c400f9686","tid":661112,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"比賓賓整一樣好似馬拉咁keep唔到水準執笠"},{"pid":"89194a8a5e81e368987be7bdaea62805766f20d5","tid":661112,"uid":71708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得Jollibee睇落好摺 又少野食揀 上次行完入去覺得唔對路走返出黎 中環個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fbb3be5f8eb24ef57a714f9a8ec2fad04c159b","tid":661112,"uid":123308,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"如果只係講雞同可樂，<br />\nJollibee 啲雞至少比 KFC 熟得透徹，<br />\n百事可樂唔會斟到連個蓋都有，<br />\n係幾好食<br />\n<br />\n之前菲律賓總統嚟香港都要食返自己家鄉 Jollibee <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529f97f3c4584e9b0400f20b5